np, here's what I came up with (based on code @ the start of this ticket)

``` python
class DictChoice(click.Choice):
    def __init__(self, choices):
        self.choices_dict = choices
        click.Choice.__init__(self, choices.keys())

    def convert(self, value, param, ctx):
        if value is None:
            return None
        initial_value = super(DictChoice, self).convert(value, param, ctx)
        return self.choices_dict.get(initial_value)
```
